      "rationale": "Validation testing conducted at a single load configuration per ASTM F1717 standard protocol. Although the standard specifies a single compression-bending configuration, no additional load levels or alternative boundary configurations were explored. Achieved level limited to Gradation 2; required level is Gradation 3 for this model risk level. This gap is acknowledged and accepted on the basis that ASTM F1717 is the regulatory reference standard for this device class."
